t dissolved due to the fire attacks launched at her by the Heavenly Empress.  \n|-\n| Peng Yang || Chief Peony (\u7261\u4e39\u82b3\u4e3b) || Head of the Pavilion chiefs.   \n|- \n| Ma Jing || Chief Begonia (\u6d77\u68e0\u82b3\u4e3b) ||\n|-\n| Wen Luhan || Chief Magnolia (\u7389\u5170\u82b3\u4e3b) ||  \n|-\n| Furou Meiqi<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-10-12/doc-ifymviyp0362456.shtml|title=\u4ed8\u67d4\u7f8e\u7426\u300a\u9999\u871c\u300b\u6740\u9752 \u9970\u6f14\u4e24\u89d2\u671f\u5f85\u9ad8|date=October 12, 2017|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref> || Rourou (\u8089\u8089)<br>Qianghuo (\u7f8c\u6d3b) ||  A succulent plant sprite. <br>Jin Mi's close friend, who died saving Jin Mi from Qiongqi's attacks, but later revives and accompanies Jin Mi in her mortal trial.  \n|- \n| Ning Wentong || Lao Hu (\u8001\u80e1) || Carrot sprite. An elder of the Flower realm. \n|-\n| Xia Yiyao || Lianqiao (\u5ec9\u6641) || A flower sprite. \n|-\n| Wu Wenxuan || Pavilion Chief (\u82b3\u4e3b) || \n|-\n| Duan Yu || Pavilion Chief (\u82b3\u4e3b) || \n|}\n\n====Demon realm==== \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:13%\"|Actor !! style=\"width:20%\"|Character !! Introduction  \n|-\n| Lu Yong || King Yancheng (\u7131\u57ce\u738b) || Ruler of the Demon realm.  \n|- \n| Yao Qingren<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-10-18/doc-ifymvuyt3511211.shtml|title=\u59da\u6e05\u4ec1\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u6740\u9752 \u535e\u57ce\u738b\u4fa0\u809d\u4e49\u80c6|date=October 18, 2017|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref> || King Biancheng (\u535e\u57ce\u738b)|| Liuying's father.\n|-\n| Song Yunhao || King Gucheng (\u56fa\u57ce\u738b) || Am ambitious man who aims to usurp the throne. \n|-\n| Wang Siyu || Chishou (\u70bd\u72e9) || Son of King Yancheng.\n|-\n| Li Silang || Xuanshou (\u70ab\u72e9) ||  Son of King Yancheng.\n|-\n| Hu Mianyang || Qiongqi (\u7a77\u5947) || A ferocious and legendary beast.  \n|- \n|}\n\n====Mortal realm====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:13%\"|Actor !! style=\"width:20%\"|Character !! Introduction  \n|- \n| Sun Ning || Lord Nanping (\u5357\u5e73\u4faf) || A royal of Huaiwu Kingdom. <br>Suihe's father in the human realm.<br> He aims to kill Xufeng during his mortal trial and usurp the throne. \n|-\n| Zhou Yihua || Chancellor Fu (\u5085\u76f8) || Chancellor of the Huaiwu Kingdom. \n|-\n| Tuo Gufeng || General Ji Chong (\u504f\u5c06\u9f50\u51b2) || Lord Nanping's subordinate. \n|- \n| Wen Jing || Jingjie (\u8346\u82a5) || Elder of the Healer tribe.<br>She adopted Jin Mi as a child during her mortal trial. \n|}\n\n==Production==\nThe series began filming in June 2017, and wrapped up in October 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20170616/019083.htm#p=1|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u5f00\u673a \u6768\u7d2b\u9093\u4f26\u5f00\u542f\u4e09\u751f\u60c5\u7f18|date=June 16, 2017|website=Tencent|language=zh}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20171016/026658.htm|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u6740\u9752 \u5320\u5fc3\u72ec\u8fd0\u7f14\u9020\u7cbe\u5267\u54c1\u76f8|date=October 16, 2017|website=Tencent|language=zh}}</ref>\n\n==Soundtrack== \n{{Tracklist\n| collapsed = \n| total_length = \n| all_writing = \n| all_lyrics = \n| all_music = \n| arranger_credits = \n| extra_column = Singers\n| title1 = Unsullied (\u4e0d\u67d3)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/yneidi/2018-02-12/doc-ifyrpeic8842417.shtml|title=\u6bdb\u4e0d\u6613\u5f71\u89c6\u521d\u732e\u58f0\u300a\u4e0d\u67d3\u300bMV\u4e0a\u7ebf \u8428\u9876\u9876\u4e3a\u5176\u5b9a\u5236|date=February 12, 2018|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref>\n| note1 = Opening theme song\n| lyrics1 = Hai Lei\n| music1 = Jason Hong\n| arranger1 = \n| extra1 = Mao Buyi (version 1)<br>[[Sa Dingding]] (version 2)<br>Jian Hongyi (version 3)\n| title2 = Upwards to the Moon (\u5de6\u624b\u6307\u6708)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/a/20180724/43076740_0.shtml|