954\n|1\n|1.51\t\n|5.58\n|1\n|-\n|60-61\n|September 3, 2018\n|1.358\t\n|5.073\n|1\n|1.64\t\n|6.46\n|1\n|-\n|62-63\n|September 4, 2018\n|1.322\t\n|5.093\n|1\n|1.64\t\n|6.36\n|1\n|-\n|Average\n|{{NA}}\n|1.301\n|4.82\n|{{NA}}\n|\n|\n|{{NA}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Reception ==\nThis drama was commercially successful, placing first among audience ratings in its time slot and exceeded 15 billion views.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.huanqiu.com/movie/yingshi-neidi/2018-08/12815529.html|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u83b7\u6c5f\u82cf\u536b\u89c62018\u6536\u89c6\u5267\u738b|date=August 24, 2018|website=Huanqiu|language=zh}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zhjjnet.com/entertainment/show/12864.html|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u300b\u5c06\u6536\u5b98\uff0c\u6536\u89c6\u7387\u78342\u521b\u65b0\u9ad8\uff0c\u6691\u671f\u7b2c2\u90e8\u7f51\u64ad\u7834\u767e\u4ebf\u5927\u5267\u8bde\u751f|date=September 2, 2018|website=Huanqiu Fengyun Website|language=zh}}</ref>\nIt also received positive reviews, scoring a 7.7 on Douban.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sc.people.com.cn/n2/2018/0816/c345488-31940084.html|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b7.6\u5206\u7ad9\u7a33\u6691\u671f\u6536\u89c6C\u4f4d|date=August 16, 2018|website=People Daily|language=zh}}</ref> The drama was praised for its light-hearted yet grounded storyline,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://epaper.tianjinwe.com/tjrb/html/2018-08/05/content_49543_314601.htm|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u5267\u60c5\u8f7b\u677e\u89e3\u538b\uff08\u56fe\uff09|date=August 5, 2018|website=Tianjin Newspaper|language=zh}}</ref> high production quality of beautiful cinematography and exquisite costumes; as well as the tight pacing of the plot and excellent performance of the actors.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://data.chinaxwcb.com/epaper2018/epaper/d6819/d6b/201808/90502.html|title=\u4ed9\u4fa0\u5267\u518d\u8d77\"\u98ce\u4e91\"|date=August 21, 2018|website=\u4e2d\u56fd\u65b0\u95fb\u51fa\u7248\u5e7f\u7535\u62a5|language=zh}}</ref> \n\nHowever later on, the series received criticism from many viewers about the extortionate amount of focus on the second male lead's storyline and background story, and his increased screentime compared to the main leads. Further, there was also much controversy surrounding the production company's decision to use a combination of two scripts, which complicated the writing credits.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/zl/bagua/2018-08-27/doc-ihifuvph8206736.shtml|title=\u6ce8\u6c34\u52a0\u620f\uff01\u300a\u9999\u871c\u300b\u8981\u628a\u4e00\u624b\u597d\u724c\u6253\u70c2\u5417\uff1f|date=August 27, 2018|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Wuzhi |title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u300b\u88ab\u8d28\u7591\u6ce8\u6c34\uff0c\u7f16\u5267\u53d1\u6587\u7529\u9505 |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/zz/2018-09-02/doc-ihinpmnr6224669.shtml |website=Sina |publisher=Sina |accessdate=6 August 2019|date=2018-09-02 }}</ref> Claims about extra screentime were later refuted by producer Liu Ning, who stated that a good drama should not simply revolve around the male lead and female lead.<ref>{{cite web |last1=He |first1=Yuan |title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u300b\u5236\u7247\u4eba\u56de\u5e94\u6ce8\u6c34\u4e89\u8bae \u900f\u9732\u5c06\u62cd\u7b2c\u4e8c\u90e8 |url=https://k.sina.com.cn/article_1644855075_620a7f2302000e4yh.html |website=Sina |publisher=Sina |accessdate=6 August 2019|date=2018-10-27 }}</ref>\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!  Awards  !! Category !! Nominated work !! Result !! Ref.\n|-\n|rowspan=2|24th [[Huading Awards]]\n|Best Actor (Ancient Drama)||[[Deng Lun]]||{{nom}}||rowspan=2|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.163.com/18/1022/11/DUNIG0DK000380EO.html|title=\u534e\u9f0e\u5956\u63d0\u540d\u516c\u5e03 \u300a\u548c\u5e73\u996d\u5e97\u300b\u300a\u5f52\u53bb\u6765\u300b\u95ea\u8000\u699c\u5355|date=October 22, 2018|website=Netease|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Actress (Ancient Drama)||[[Yang Zi (actress)|Yang Zi]]||{{nom}}\n|-\n|7th [[iQiyi]] All-Star Carnival||Popularity Award (Actor)||rowspan=2|[[Deng Lun]]||{{Won}}||<ref>{{cite web |title=2019\u7231\u5947\u827a\u5c16\u53eb\u4e4b\u591c\u5168\u7a0b\u56de\u987e 2019\u7231\u5947\u827a\u5c16\u53eb\u4e4b\u591c\u5b8c\u6574\u83b7\u5956\u540d\u5355 |url=http://www.fengfeng.cc/news/zhnews/2018-12-02/31733.html |website=Fengfeng.cc}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=3|12th [[Tencent]] Video Star Awards||Popular TV Actor||{{won}}||<ref name=two>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20181218/013151.htm|title=\u817e\u8baf\u89c6\u9891\u661f\u5149\u76db\u5178\uff1aBaby\u7f8e\u6768\u8d85\u8d8a\u840c\uff0c\u8001\u620f\u9aa8\u4eec\u6700\u6709\u8303\u513f|date=18 December 2018|website=Tencent|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n|Popular TV Actress of the Year||[[Yang Zi (actress)|Yang Zi]]||{{won}}||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/a/20181220/43154857_0.shtml|title=\u6768\u7d2b\u83b7\u4eba\u6c14\u5973\u6f14\u5458\u5956|date=December 20, 2018|website=ifeng|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n|Top Ten Series || rowspan=2|''Ashes of Love''||{{Won}} || <ref name=two /> \n|- \n|Entertainment Capital The 2nd Golden Pebble Award||Best Episode Project||{{Won}} || rowspan=3|<ref>{{cite web |title=Heavy Sweetness , Ash-Like Frost |url=https://www.weibo.com/6157271643/H7PRK3qJ0 |website=Weibo |publisher=Heavy Sweetness , Ash-Like Frost |accessdate=December 18, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Media Internal Reference - TV Guide 2018 Mobile Influence Summit Forum||The Most Influential Drama Trader of the 2018 Fingertips List||Liu Ning||{{won}}\n|-\n|The Most Mobile TV Drama of the 2018 Fingertips List||rowspan=2|''Ashes of Love''||{{Won}}\n|-\n|Weibo Taiwanese TV series||Weibo 2018 Influence Drama||{{Won}}||<ref>{{cite web |title=Weibo TV Series |url=https://www.weibo.com/52dsj |date=December 23, 2018|website=weibo.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|V Influence Summit 2018||2018 Most Best Drama Producer||Liu Ning||{{Won}}||<ref>{{cite web |title=V Influence Summit 2018 |url=https://www.weibo.com/u/5742418474 |website=Sina}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=6|TV Drama Award 2018 (Weibo TV Series)||Top 10 Most Popular Drama||''Ashes of Love''||Top 3||rowspan=6|<ref>{{cite web |title=Weibo TV Series |url=https://www.weibo.com/5406006781/H9vwa0reb |website=Weibo}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=2|Top 10 Most Popular Actor||[[Deng Lun]]||Top 3\n|-\n|[[Yang Zi (actress)|Yang Zi]]||Top 5\n|-\n|Most Popular Screen Couple||[[Yang Zi (actress)|Yang Zi]] and [[Deng Lun]]||{{Won}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2|The Most Popular Hot Stalk||\"\"Have you ever loved me...\" \"Never\"||{{Won}}\n|-\n|\"You are finally my ugly wife.\"||Top 5\n|-\n|rowspan=3|Weibo Award Ceremony||Weibo Annual Hot Drama Honor||''Ashes of Love''||{{won}}||rowspan=3|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://slide.ent.sina.com.cn/star/slide_4_704_303814.html|title=2018\u5fae\u535a\u4e4b\u591c \u5510\u5ae3\u79e6\u5c9a\u4f58\u8bd7\u66fc\u9a6c\u601d\u7eaf\u6768\u7d2b\u5a1c\u624e\u83b7\u5e74\u5ea6\u5973\u795e|date=January 11, 2019|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n|Weibo Popular Artist||[[Deng Lun]]||{{won}}\n|-\n|Weibo Goddess||rowspan=3|[[Yang Zi (actress)|Yang Zi]]||{{won}}\n|-\n|[[Tencent]] Entertainment White Paper||Popular Television Actress of the Year||{{won}}||<ref>{{cite web |title=\u6768\u7d2b\u83b7\u817e\u8baf\u5a31\u4e50\u767d\u76ae\u4e66\u7535\u89c6\u5267\u5e74\u5ea6\u4e4b\u661f\uff0c\u7acb\u8a932019\u5e74\u6212\u706b\u9505 |url=https://new.qq.com/cmsn/20190117/20190117008570.html?pc |website=Tencent |accessdate=January 17, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=4|Film and TV Role Model 2018 Annual General Rating||Popular Actress||{{won}}||rowspan=4|<ref>{{cite web |title=\"\u5f71\u89c6\u699c\u6837\u00b72018\u5e74\u5ea6\u603b\u8bc4\u699c\"\u699c\u5355\u63ed\u6653 \u5f71\u89c6\u5927\u5496\u9f50\u805a\u8bba\u575b\u8bdd\u521d\u5fc3 |url=http://ent.people.com.cn/n1/2019/0128/c1012-30593505.html |website=People's Daily |accessdate=January 28, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|Annual Drama Producer||Liu Ning||{{won}}\n|-\n|Annual Drama Director||Zhu Ruibin||{{won}}\n|-\n|Annual Drama Series Screenwriter||Ma Jia||{{won}} \n|-\n|Influence of Recreational Responsibilities Awards\n|TV Drama of the Year\n|''Ashes of Love'' \n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://k.sina.com.cn/article_1822398137_p6c9f96b902700hhny.html|title=2019\u6587\u5a31\u8d23\u4efb\u5f71\u54cd\u529b\u83b7\u5956\u540d\u5355\u51fa\u7089|date=March 28, 2019|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref>\n|- \n| The Third Internet Film Festival || Most Capable Actress || [[Kathy Chow]] || {{won}} || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/336338547_141588|title=\u7b2c\u4e09\u5c4a\u7f51\u5f71\u76db\u5178\u76db\u5927\u843d\u5e55\uff0c\u91d1\u7261\u4e39\u5956\u5404\u5956\u9879\u9010\u4e00\u63ed\u6653 |date=August 25, 2019|website=Sohu|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Seoul International Drama Awards]]||Most Popular Foreign Drama of the Year||''Ashes of Love''||{{Won}}||<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.seouldrama.org/EN/infoCenter/InformationView.aspx?pageNo=1&idx=921|title=Seoul International Drama Awards8|website=www.seouldrama.org|access-date=2019-08-29}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==International broadcast==\n* {{flag|Malaysia}} - [[8TV (Malaysia)]] (26 November 2018)\n* {{flag|Singapore}} - E-Le (10 December 2018)\n* {{flag|South Korea}} - [[tvN Asia]] (22 January 2019)\n* {{flag|Hong Kong}} and {{flag|Taiwan}}\n* {{flag|Myanmar}}\n* {{flag|Cambodia}} on Ctv8 hd\n* Latin America on Netflix\n* United States on Netflix\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%A6%99%E8%9C%9C%E6%B2%89%E6%B2%89%E7%83%AC%E5%A6%82%E9%9C%9C/18813778 ''Ashes of Love''] on [[Baidu]] \n{{Jiangsu Television Happy Theatre}}\n\n[[Category:Chinese romantic fantasy television series]]\n[[Category:Television programs based on Chinese novels]]\n[[Category:2018 Chinese television series debuts]]\n[[Category:Television series by Perfect World Pictures]]\n[[Category:Xianxia television series]]\n[[Category:2018 Chinese television series endings]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = Ashes of Love\n| image                    =  Xiangmichenchen.jpg<!-- include ALT text per [[WP:ALT]] guideline -->\n| caption                  = Drama poster  \n| show_name_2              = Heavy Sweetness, Ash-like Frost \n| genre                    = {{ubl|[[Xianxia novel|Xianxia]] |[[Fantasy film|Fantasy]]|[[romance novel|Romance]]}} \n| based_on                 = {{based on|''Heavy Sweetness, Ash-like Frost''|Dian Xian}}\n| writer                   = Ma Jia<br>Xu Zishan<br>Liu Gelin<br>Chen Lusha<br>Zhang Yuan'ang \n| director                 = Zhu Ruibin  \n| starring                 = {{ubl|[[Yang Zi (actress)|Yang Zi]]|[[Deng Lun]]|[[Luo Yunxi]]|Wang Yifei|[[Chen Yuqi]]|Zou Tingwei}}  \n| voices                   = \n| opentheme                = \n| endtheme                 = \n| composer                 = [[Sa Dingding]]<ref name=sdd>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ce.cn/news/201708/23/t20170823_25238157.shtml|title=\u8428\u9876\u9876\u6311\u5927\u6881\u62c5\u4efb\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u97f3\u4e50\u5236\u4f5c\u603b\u76d1|date=August 23, 2017|website=\u4e2d\u56fd\u7ecf\u6d4e\u7f51|language=ko}}</ref> \n| country                  = China\n| language                 = Mandarin \n| num_seasons              = 1\n| num_episodes             = 63 (TV), 60 (DVD)\n| runtime                  = 45 mins \n| producer                 =  \n| executive_producer       = {{ubl|Liu Ning|Zhang Yancheng<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.163.com/18/0113/15/D81QS4UB000333J5.html|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u6740\u9752 \u5f20\u664f\u8bda\u62c5\u4efb\u6267\u884c\u5236\u7247\u4eba|date=January 13, 2018|website=Netease|language=zh}}</ref>}} \n| editor                   = \n| location                 = [[Hengdian World Studios]]  \n| cinematography           = \n| company                  = {{ubl|[[Perfect World Pictures]]|Omnijoi Media Corporation|Happy Era Media|Kunchi Pictures|Chongqing Shengmei}} \n| channel                  = [[Jiangsu TV]]\n| picture_format           = [[1080i]] ([[HDTV]])\n| audio_format             = [[Stereo]]\n| first_run                = China\n| first_aired              = {{Start date|2018|8|2}}\n| last_aired               = {{End date|2018|9|4}}\n| preceded_by              = \n| followed_by              = \n| related                  = \n| website                  = \n| website_title            = \n| production_website       = \n| production_website_title = \n}}\n'''''Ashes of Love'''''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/201808/23/WS5b7e1b07a310add14f3874f7.html|title=Stills of fantasy drama 'Ashes of Love' released|date=August 23, 2018|website=China Daily}}</ref> ({{zh|c=\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c}}) is a 2018 Chinese television series based on the novel ''Heavy Sweetness, Ash-like Frost'' by Dian Xian.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-03-08/doc-ifycaafm5495196.shtml?cre=entpc&mod=f&loc=10&r=1&doct=0&rfunc=78|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u5267\u7248\u542f\u52a8 \u5c0f\u8bf4\u539f\u8457\u4f5c\u8005\u52a0\u76df|website=Sina|date=March 8, 2017|language=zh}}</ref> It stars [[Yang Zi (actress)|Yang Zi]] and [[Deng Lun]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-06-20/doc-ifyhfnqa4484042.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u9996\u66dd\u5b9a\u5986\u6d77\u62a5 \u518d\u6380\u4ed9\u4fa0\u5947\u5e7b|date=June 20, 2017|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/a/20180716/43069269_0.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u6768\u7d2b\u9093\u4f26\u52a8\u60c5\u6f14\u7ece\"\u5343\u5e74\u4e4b\u604b\"|website=ifeng|language=zh|date=July 16, 2018}}</ref> The series premiered on [[Jiangsu TV]] starting August 2, 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.jstv.com/a/20180720/153205073471.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u573a\u666f\u7279\u6548\u83b7\u8d5e \u82b1\u8bed\u5e7b\u5883\u7a81\u7834\u89c6\u89c9\u60f3\u8c61|date=July 20, 2018|website=Jiangsu TV|language=zh}}</ref>\n\nAs of January 2019, the series has reached 15 billion views.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://xw.qq.com/cmsid/20190109A0C6GG00|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u300b\u7f51\u64ad\u91cf\u6b63\u5f0f\u7a81\u7834150\u4ebf\uff01|website=Tencent|language=zh|date=January 9, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Synopsis==\nThe Floral Goddess gives birth to a daughter who she names Jin Mi. She shares with her fairy attendants that she is fearful that her daughter will suffer a great love trial within the first 10,000 years of her life. To keep her daughter safe and from meeting the same fate as herself, she does two things: first, she gives Jin Mi a magical pill to keep her from feeling and expressing romantic love; second, she forbids her attendants from divulging Jin Mi\u2019s identity as the daughter of the Floral Goddess to anyone. The Floral Goddess then passes away, tearfully leaving her daughter in the care of the Floral Fairies.\n\nDespite consuming the pill and the protection of the Floral Fairies, Jin Mi unwittingly becomes entangled in a love triangle involving two brothers, Fire God Xufeng and Night God Runyu, sons of the Heavenly Emperor. Outside forces push and pull the three to and from another, culminating at the wedding of Jin Mi and Runyu. During her and Runyu\u2019s wedding ceremony, Jin Mi stabs Xufeng because she mistakenly believes he is the one who killed her father and stepmother. It is at this moment that the magical pill shatters, allowing Jin Mi to realize that she loves Xufeng. Runyu also successfully ascends the throne of the Heavenly Realm when his father dies. \n\nJin Mi does everything she can to bring Xufeng back to life, even giving up her ability to see color, but after doing so, finds that he treats her coldly. Xufeng becomes Demon King and continues to ignore her attempts to explain the truth and her romantic feelings for him, instead turning his attention to Suihe, who has desired to be his bride since they were young. Eventually, Suihe admits to killing Jin Mi\u2019s father and stepmother after being confronted with evidence and is banished. Xufeng is tricked into marrying a spellbound Jin Mi but their love is revealed to be true. This invokes the wrath of Runyu, who brings a large army to force Jin Mi to come back with him and honor a marriage agreement between their fathers. A war breaks out. \n\nJin Mi, finally understanding her fate, sacrifices herself to end the war by jumping in the middle of the brothers\u2019 powerful attacks. After her death, the two make amends and Xufeng encourages Runyu to remain Heavenly Emperor. Wishing to be reunited with Jin Mi, Xufeng leaves the Demon Realm and searches for her. Eventually, Jin Mi is reborn as a mortal and Xufeng finds her, intercepting her when she is about to marry someone else. She still has her memories from when she was a fairy but no longer can see color after giving it up for Xufeng\u2019s revival. They become husband and wife and are shown to have a son, Tang Yue, who narrates the epilogue.\n\n==Cast==\n===Main=== \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:13%\"|Actor !! style=\"width:20%\"|Character !! Introduction  \n|-\n| [[Yang Zi (actress)|Yang Zi]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/a/20170616/42949094_0.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u5f00\u673a \u6768\u7d2b\u4e3a\u620f\u51cf\u80a5\u505c\u4e0d\u4e0b\u6765|website=iFeng|language=zh|date=July 16, 2017}}</ref><br> (\u6768\u7d2b)  || Jin Mi (\u9526\u89c5) || A grape sprite, whose real identity is a six-petal frost flower fairy.<br> Daughter of the Flower Goddess and Water God. <br> She is naive and altruistic, but does not understand the true meaning of \"love\" due to the magical pill she was given at birth. <br>She later becomes the Water Goddess following her father's death.\n|-\n| [[Deng Lun]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20170427/021485.htm|title=\u9093\u4f26\u786e\u8ba4\u51fa\u6f14\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b \u5168\u65b0\u5236\u4f5c\u6a21\u5f0f|website=Tencent|language=zh|date=April 27, 2017}}</ref><br>(\u9093\u4f26)  || Xufeng (\u65ed\u51e4)|| Second prince of the Heaven realm; the Fire God and God of War (Phoenix).<br> He becomes the Demon King after his revival from death.\n|-  \n| [[Luo Yunxi]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-06-16/doc-ifyhfnqa4370715.shtml|title=\u7f57\u4e91\u7199\u300a\u9999\u871c\u300b\u51fa\u6f14\u591c\u795e\u6da6\u7389 \u79f0\u7ec8\u4e8e\"\u60c5\u573a\u5931\u610f\"|website=Sina|date=June 16, 2017|language=zh}}</ref><br> (\u7f57\u4e91\u7199) || Runyu (\u6da6\u7389)|| Eldest prince of the Heaven realm; the Night God (Dragon). <br> A gentle and calm person. Due to his lowly birth, he has never truly gained respect in the Heaven realm since young. He later becomes embroiled in a political battle for the throne after his mother's death, and ascends the throne to become the Heavenly Emperor.  \n|-\n| Wang Yifei<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ent.china.com/movie/tv/11015529/20180810/33535005.html|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u738b\u4e00\u83f2\u604b\u9093\u4f26 \u7f51\u53cb\uff1a\u5929\u754c\u7b2c\u4e00\u552f\u996d|website=China|date=August 10, 2018|language=zh}}</ref><br> (\u738b\u4e00\u83f2)||Suihe (\u7a57\u79be) || Princess of the Bird Tribe; the Peacock immortal.<br> Proud and arrogant, she wields great responsibility in securing power within the Bird tribe. She becomes crazed due to her unrequited love for Xufeng, which caused her to commit many cruel deeds.\n|-\n|[[Chen Yuqi]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-06-16/doc-ifyhfnrf9230348.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u9648\u94b0\u742a\u6311\u6218\u9b54\u65cf\u516c\u4e3b\u5f81\u6218\u6c99\u573a|website=Sina|date=June 16, 2017|language=zh}}</ref><br> (\u9673\u923a\u742a) || Liuying (\u938f\u82f1) || Demon Princess.<br> A cheerful and forthright girl, and a heroic warrior. She has a tragic romantic relationship with her bodyguard, Muci.\n|-\n| Zou Tingwei<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/a/20170619/42949581_0.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u5f00\u673a \u90b9\u5ef7\u5a01\u51fa\u6f14\u795e\u79d8\u4eba\u5947\u9e22|website=iFeng|date=June 19, 2017|language=zh}}</ref><br> (\u9112\u5ef7\u5a01) || Qiyuan (\u5947\u9e22)<br>Muci (\u66ae\u8fad) || A reaper who has double identities.<br>He was forced to commit evil deeds for the Heavenly empress due to her control and manipulation, but remains kind at heart. He has a tragic romantic relationship with Liuying.\n|-\n|}\n\n===Supporting=== \n====Heaven realm==== \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:13%\"|Actor !! style=\"width:20%\"|Character !! Introduction  \n|-\n| He Zhonghua<ref name=cast /> || Taiwei (\u592a\u5fae) || Heavenly emperor (Dragon). Ruler of the Heaven realm.<br> A selfish and possessive man who is adept at making use of other people to achieve his goals.\n|-\n| [[Kathy Chow]]<ref name=cast>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-09-22/doc-ifymfcih2430418.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u66dd\u7167 \u5468\u6d77\u5a9a\u4f55\u4e2d\u534e\u5f3a\u52bf\u52a0\u76df|date=September 22, 2017|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref> || Tuyao (\u837c\u59da) || Heavenly empress (Phoenix). Ruler of the Bird tribe. <br> A scheming and cruel woman who caused the death of the Flower deity, and schemes to get rid of Jin Mi and Runyu. \n|- \n| Xia Zhiyuan<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20170616/033244.htm|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u5f00\u673a \u590f\u5fd7\u8fdc\u6f14\u7ece\u6700\u840c\u6708\u8001|website=Tencent|date=June 16, 2017|language=zh}}</ref> || Dan Zhu (\u4e39\u6731)<br>Match Maker|| The Moon Immortal Yuexia (Fox). <br>Taiwei's younger brother; Xufeng and Runyu's uncle.<br> Known for his mischievous personality and youthful looks, he is in charge of love and marriage of all mortal beings. He is earnest in bringing Xufeng and Jin Mi together as a couple.\n|-  \n| Wang Renjun<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-06-20/doc-ifyhfnqa4494544.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u300b\u6a2a\u5e97\u5f00\u673a \u738b\u4ec1\u541b\u9970\u4ed9\u5bb6\u7f8e\u7537\u5b50\u6c34\u795e\u6d1b\u9716|date=June 20, 2017|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref> || Luolin (\u6d1b\u9716) || Water immortal.<br> Jin Mi's father and Zifen's lover. <br> An elegant and refined man who keeps himself out of worldly affairs, but is loyal and helpful to those in need.    \n|-\n| Wang Yuanke || Lin Xiu (\u4e34\u79c0)||  Wind immortal. <br> Luo Lin's betrothed wife.<br> A kind and gentle woman who is a good friend of Zifen and treats Jin Mi as her own.\n|-\n| Fan Mianlin || Suli (\u7c0c\u79bb) || Dragon Fish Princess. Lord of Dongting lake.<br> Runyu's birth mother, who gave birth to him after being impregnated by the Heavenly Emperor due to her resemblance with Zifen. She schemed for years to seek revenge on the Heavenly Empress for killing her tribe.  \n|-\n|Liao Jingfeng || Lord Puchi (\u6251\u54e7\u541b) <br>Yanyou (\u5f66\u4f51) || Snake immortal. <br> After getting banished from the Heaven realm, he was adopted by Suli and became one of her god-sons. He befriended Jin Mi after saving her from the attacks of Qiongqi thousand of years ago.  \n|- \n| Du Yuchen<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20171017/031811.htm#p=1|title=\u675c\u96e8\u5bb8\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u6740\u9752 \u89d2\u8272\u4e30\u76c8\u9971\u6ee1|date=October 17, 2017|website=Tencent|language=zh}}</ref> || Kuang Lu (\u909d\u9732)|| Daughter of Immortal Taiji. <br> She voluntary becomes Runyu's subordinate due to her admiration for him, and remains loyal to him through thick and thin.        \n|-\n| [[Sa Dingding]]<ref name=sdd /> || Immortal Yuanji (\u7f18\u673a\u4ed9\u5b50) || An immortal who is in charge of the fate and destiny of human beings.  \n|-\n| Zhang Junran<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2017-10-17/doc-ifymvuyt2667086.shtml|title=\u300a\u9999\u871c\u6c89\u6c89\u70ec\u5982\u971c\u300b\u5f20\u94a7\u7136\u6740\u9752 \u597d\u6027\u683c\u4eba\u8bbe\u6696|date=October 17, 2017|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref> || Lord Liaoyuan (\u71ce\u539f\u541b)<br> Qin Tong (\u79e6\u6f7c) || Xufeng's personal guard.    \n|- \n| Li Yixuan || [[Doumu|Lord Doumu]] (\u6597\u59c6\u5143\u541b) || Luolin, Lin Xiu and Zifen's teacher.   \n|- \n| Li Yongtian ||  [[Daode Tianzun|Taishang Laojun]] (\u592a\u4e0a\u8001\u541b) ||\n|-\n| Zhang Shihong || Immortal Taiji (\u592a\u5df3\u4ed9\u4eba) ||  \n|- \n| He Junlin || Thunder God Yunxiang (\u4e91\u54cd\u96f7\u516c) ||\n|-\n| Liu Siying || Lightning Goddess Shengguang (\u5723\u5149\u7535\u6bcd) || \n|-\n| Li Xuefeng || Rat Immortal (\u9f20\u4ed9) || Leader of the Zodiac immortals.<br> Suli's subordinate, who helps her collect information in the Heaven realm. \n|- \n| Zhang Xiaoyang || Liao Ting (\u4e86\u542c) || Xufeng's subordinate.   \n|-\n| Cui Binbin || Fei Xu (\u98de\u7d6e) || Xufeng's subordinate. \n|-\n| Zheng Ge || Po Jun (\u7834\u519b) || A heavenly soldier recruited by Xufeng. \n|- \n| Fu Hongsheng || Yinque (\u9690\u96c0) || Elder of Bird tribe. \n|-\n| Dong Xiaobai || Queling (\u96c0\u7075) || Suihe's subordinate. \n|- \n| Liu Haochen || Lianchao (\u5ec9\u6641) || Brother of Taiwei, Tuyao's first love.\n|- \n| Liu Xiangping || Earth deity (\u571f\u5730\u4ed9) || \n|-\n| Zhong Sutong || Little fairy (\u5c0f\u4ed9\u5973) ||  \n|}\n\n====Flower realm==== \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:13%\"|Actor !! style=\"width:20%\"|Character !! Introduction  \n|-\n| Zhang Yanyan || Zifen (\u6893\u82ac) || Floral Goddess. Ruler of the Floral Realm.<br>Jin Mi's mother. <br>She died after her spirit dissolved due to the fire attacks launched at her by the Heavenly Empress.