ilmaz|Sars\u0131lmaz Arms]].\n|-\n|[[M16 rifle|M16]]<ref name=armyrecog/>|| [[File:M16a1m16a2m4m16a45wi.jpg|150px]] || [[5.56\u00d745mm NATO]] || {{USA}} || M16A4 is used by commando units.\n|-\n|[[FN SCAR|SCAR]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.haberdar.com/turkiye-belcika-dan-4-yilda-12-milyon-euro-luk-silah-satin-aldi-1341116-haberi |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-04-05 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407083540/http://www.haberdar.com/turkiye-belcika-dan-4-yilda-12-milyon-euro-luk-silah-satin-aldi-1341116-haberi |archivedate=7 April 2014 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>|| [[File:Scar H Standard.jpg|150px]] || [[7.62\u00d751mm NATO]] || {{BEL}}<br>{{USA}} || SCAR-H variant in use by [[Special Forces Command (Turkey)|Special Forces Command]].\n|-\n|[[Steyr AUG|AUG]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://docplayer.biz.tr/11762626-Suriye-deki-muhalif-orgutlerin-askeri-kapasitesi-silah-turleri-ve-silahlanma.html|title=SUR\u0130YE'DEK\u0130 MUHAL\u0130F \u00d6RG\u00dcTLER\u0130N ASKER\u0130 KAPAS\u0130TES\u0130: S\u0130LAH T\u00dcRLER\u0130 VE S\u0130LAHLANMA - PDF|website=docplayer.biz.tr|accessdate=11 May 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513063841/http://docplayer.biz.tr/11762626-Suriye-deki-muhalif-orgutlerin-askeri-kapasitesi-silah-turleri-ve-silahlanma.html|archive-date=13 May 2016|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>|| [[File:Steyr-AUG.jpeg|150px]] || [[5.56\u00d745mm NATO]] || {{AUT}} || AUG A2 variant in use by [[Special Forces Command (Turkey)|Special Forces Command]].\n|-\n|[[IMI Tavor TAR-21|TAR-21]]<ref name=\"dha\">{{cite web|url=http://www.dha.com.tr/fotogaleri/orj/27057_1885_03102012_4.jpg|title=Image: 27057_1885_03102012_4.jpg, (2400 \u00d7 2271 px) \u2013 GENELKURMAY BASKANI ORGENERAL NECDET OZEL VE KARA KUKUVVETLERI KOMUTANI ORGENERAL HAYRI KIVRIKOGLU INCELEMELERDE BULUNMAK UZERE ERZURUM'A GELDI.|publisher=dha.com.tr|accessdate=5 September 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923214355/http://www.dha.com.tr/fotogal