ry radar, Kyiv 2018, 06.jpg|216x216px]]||{{TUR}} || Counter-Mortar Radar || \n|-\n|SERHAT II\n|\n|{{TUR}}\n|Counter-Mortar Radar\n|Deliveries continuing 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://c4news.me/RVNnl|title=SERHAT II in Inventory|website=c4news.me|accessdate=2020-01-26}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Electronic Warfare ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Model\n!Image\n!Origin\n!Description\n!Quantity\n|-\n|MILKAR 3A3\n|[https://img1.aksam.com.tr/imgsdisk/2019/08/13/130820191631551999899.jpg]\n|{{TUR}}\n|Interception of V/UHF frequencies. Project undertaken by the SSB.\n|11<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://savunmasanayist.com/2019/08/13/tskya-elektronik-harp-sistemi-teslimati/|title=TSK'ya elektronik harp sistemi teslimat\u0131|last=\u015eAH\u0130N|first=ANIL|date=2019-08-13|website=SavunmaSanayiST|language=Turkish|accessdate=2019-08-13}}</ref>\n|-\n|REDET II<ref>http://www.c4defence.com/Arsiv/korala-redetii-destegi/8940/1</ref>\n|[https://c4defence.com/ImageM/39133a86-c186-4085-a97f-4d130b59a6db.jpg]\n|{{TUR}}\n|MOBILE RADAR ELECTRONIC SUPPORT / ELECTRONIC ATTACK SYSTEM (RADAR ES/EA)\n|?\n|-\n|[[KORAL Electronic Warfare System]]<ref>https://www.yenisafak.com/dunya/baris-pinari-koral-ile-basladi-sistemin-menzili-200-km-3509713</ref>\n|[https://www.armyrecognition.com/images/stories/europe/turkey/military_equipment/koral_warfare/Koral_land-based_radar_electronic_warfare_defense_attack_system_Aselsan_Turkey_Turkish_army_military_equipment_640_001.jpg]\n|{{TUR}}\n| Electronic Support Systems (ED) and one Electronic Attack System (ET), 200km range<ref>https://www.yenisafak.com/dunya/baris-pinari-koral-ile-basladi-sistemin-menzili-200-km-3509713</ref>\n|?\n|-\n|[[ASELSAN]] RF Jammer<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aselsan.com.tr/en/capabilities/electronic-warfare-systems/electronic-warfare-self-protection-systems/rf-jammer|title=RF Jammer {{!}} ASELSAN|website=www.aselsan.com.tr|accessdate=2020-03-21}}</ref>\n|[https://www.aselsan.com.tr/478da29a-c32c-47ee-ac22-55722cf71bd9.jpg]\n|{{TUR}}\n|\n|\n