stel/karayel%20su%20idef.jpg]\n|{{TUR}}\n|10<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/teknoloji/milli-iha-karayel-10-bin-ucus-saatine-ulasti-41150333|title=Milli \u0130HA Karayel, 10 bin u\u00e7u\u015f saatine ula\u015ft\u0131|last=A.A|website=www.hurriyet.com.tr|language=tr|accessdate=2020-01-15}}</ref>\n|[[Vestel Karayel]] is a surveillance, reconnaissance and combat [[Unmanned aerial vehicle|UAV]]/UCAV \nsystem developed for the [[Turkish Armed Forces]] by [[Vestel]].\n|}\n\n=== Helicopters ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#aabccc;\"\n!Model!!Image!!Origin!!Type!!Number!!Details\n|-\n|[[TAI/AgustaWestland T-129|T-129 ATAK]]<ref name=\"tai\">{{cite web|url=https://www.tai.com.tr/en/project/atak|title=T129 ATTACK HELICOPTER - Turkish Aerospace Industries, Inc.|publisher=tai.com.tr|accessdate=5 September 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150720214143/https://www.tai.com.tr/en/project/atak|archive-date=20 July 2015|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"blogspot\">{{cite web|url=http://rewreward.blogspot.com/2012/01/turkiye-atakna-kavusuyor.html|title=Savunma ve Stratejik Analizler: T\u00fcrkiye \"ATAK\"\u0131na kavu\u015fuyor|publisher=rewreward.blogspot.com|accessdate=5 September 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722222111/http://rewreward.blogspot.com/2012/01/turkiye-atakna-kavusuyor.html|archive-date=22 July 2015|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=flightglobal1/>||[[File:BG12-1001 (14662033896).jpg|150px]]|| {{TUR}} || [[Attack helicopter]] || 50<ref>https://twitter.com/SavunmaSanayii/status/1212013066537328640</ref>|| 31 more on order. Produced by [[Turkish Aerospace Industries|TAI]].\n|-\n|[[Bell AH-1 SuperCobra|AH-1 SuperCobra]]<ref name=armyrecog/><ref name=globalsecurity/>|| [[File:AH-1W Super Cobra assigned to HMLA 167.jpg|150px]] || {{USA}} || [[Attack helicopter]] ||10<ref>https://www.savunmag\u00fcnl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc.com/2018/04/03/tsk-envanterinde-kac-saldiri-helikopteri-var/</ref> || 