ense/2017/06/16/turkish-company-delivers-6-more-drones-to-army|title=Turkish company delivers 6 more drones to army|work=DailySabah|accessdate=2017-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014133846/https://www.dailysabah.com/defense/2017/06/16/turkish-company-delivers-6-more-drones-to-army|archive-date=14 October 2017|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>|| [[File:Bayraktar TB2 Runway.jpg|150px]] || {{TUR}} || 75 || Block A and Block B variants in use.\n|-\n|[[General Atomics GNAT|GNAT]]<ref name=\"globalsecurity\" />||[[File:General Atomics I-GNAT ER.jpg|150px]]||{{USA}}|| 22 || Being replaced by local produced units.\n|-\n|[[Bayraktar Ak\u0131nc\u0131]]\n|[[File:BayraktarAk\u0131nc\u0131 Teknofest2019 (1).jpg|center|frameless|150x150px]]\n|{{TUR}}\n|2\n|\n|-\n|[[IAI Heron|Heron]]<ref name=\"iha\">{{cite web|url=http://www.iha.com.tr/gundem/turkiye-heronlarina-kavusuyor/43176|title=T\u00fcrkiye Heron'lar\u0131na kavu\u015fuyor haberi - \u0130hlas Haber Ajans\u0131|publisher=iha.com.tr|accessdate=5 September 2015}}</ref>||[[File:IAI Heron 1 in flight 2.JPEG|150px]]||{{ISR}}|| 10 || In use with upgraded [[FLIR]] by [[Aselsan]].\n|-\n|[[STM Kargu]]\n|\n|{{TUR}}\n|356\n|Mini UAV and [[Loitering munition]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/defense/2019/12/15/hundreds-of-new-generation-kamikaze-mini-drones-to-join-security-forces|title=Hundreds of new-generation kamikaze mini drones to join security forces|website=DailySabah|accessdate=2020-01-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ssb.gov.tr/urunkatalog/tr/142/|title=SSB - T\u00dcRK SAVUNMA SANAY\u0130\u0130 \u00dcR\u00dcN KATALO\u011eU|website=www.ssb.gov.tr|accessdate=2020-01-19}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Ryan Firebee|Firebee]]<ref name=\"globalsecurity\" />||[[File:Teledyne-Ryan-Firebee-hatzerim-1.jpg|150px]]||{{USA}}|| x || Used in AA target trainings.\n|-\n|TAI \u015e\u0130M\u015eEK\n|[http://www.millisavunma.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/simsek.png]\n|{{TUR}}\n|x\n|\u015e\u0130M\u015eEK ([[Thunder]]) 