 Needs Dick\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003974933&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"One Fish, Two Fish\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003974933&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"Exquisite Corpses\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003974933&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"Game Night\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003974933&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"American Data?\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003963807&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"Salute Your Sllort\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003965783&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"Men II Boyz\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003968907&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"A Starboy is Born\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003974933&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"Ghost Dad\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003974933&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"First, Do Not Farm\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003974933&Search_Code=DOCN U.S. Copyright Records database]</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | EAJN??\n| \"The Old Country\"\n| <ref>[https://cocatalog.loc.gov/cgi-bin/Pwebrecon.cgi?Search_Arg=PAu003974926&Search_C